title: [Maelstrom Bay, Surface]
description: The green waters of Maelstrom Bay stretch out in all directions.  The line of a cliff is visible on the horizon to the east.  To the west, a low coral reef rises above the wide, rolling swells.  The spray from the swells slapping against the reef is ghostly pale in the moonlight.

paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast
